Generale Bank cuts savings bond rates . Belgium ' s biggest bank Generale de Banque SA said on Wednesday it would lower the interest rates offered on its " cash bond " savings certificates from Friday . The new ( old ) rates are : One year bond 3 . 00 pct ( 3 . 10 ) Two years bond 3 . 50 pct ( 3 . 75 ) Three years bond 4 . 10 pct ( 4 . 50 ) Five years bond 5 . 00 pct ( 5 . 45 ) The bank said its move was a response to movements in market interest rates . - - Brussels Newsroom + 32 2 287 6810 , Fax + 32 2 230 7710 
